info.name: Kaedehara Kazuha Theme - Roblox
info.description: This is a follow-up to a request, I fulfil most, so go ahead and send a pic of what you want in the comments. All credits go to >Csyday< for this fanart. This code may be buggy as it's part of the base code that I'm currently still improving, do comment if there are any major issues with the UI. If you want more fixed roblox styles just click BoopBop at the top, or you can click DittoDino below for some mediocre youtube progressbars.
info.additionalInfo:
This is the Alt of DittoDino. Used in case kids decide they wanna flood /e in the chat. Disclaimers: Won't work for tablets/iPads or phones. The style not appearing/downloading bug is an issue with the extension, not the style but there are possible solutions below. Help Section Below - Read it's important . French Translated Help Section - Section d'aide traduite en français - cliquez ici. Russian/Cyrillic Translated Help Section - Русский/кириллица переведенный раздел помощи - кликните сюда. Spanish Translated Help Section - Sección de ayuda traducida al español - haga clic aquí. The Start of the English Help Section, practically an essay now. Why does it not appear/download or why does it disappear?
You have to either wait til the site fully loads in which may take a minute or two or close the browser and try again to reinstall the style, this is an issue with the extension/site, you can also try turning off and on the style through the popup of the extension, the 2nd Fix explains this, or turn the extension off and on.
It's laggy
If it's taking a while to load or the gif is stopping sometimes, it's likely a combo of your device and stylish itself, get a better device would be the solution.
Why is it so ugly?
It's poor quality, cause of roblox security policy and I have to put in the raw image, which 9 times out of 10, will be too big for the 250kb stylish limit, so I gotta make it look more pixelated since bigger pixels mean less pixels and that means less data. If you just think the theme colours are off-putting, please do suggest a better one, I'll be happy to test then implement them.
Instructions for 1st and 2nd Fixes: If you have installed the style on the new site layout, click "Check it out," and skip ahead. If not, continue reading. Go to the Roblox website and click the puzzle piece in the top right corner. Click on "Stylish." A pop-up will appear. Go to the "My Styles" tab. Read the solutions below to fix your problem. 1st Fix if it's a White Background see if you have the fixed background selected, follow the instructions above and then hover over the style and check the name of it, turn off or delete the ones that are broken with the trash bin button on the far right as multiple backgrounds at the same time won't make it work. 2nd Fix if it's the Default Roblox Theme, you probably ran into a bug, back at the top, there are some possible solutions to this. Follow the instructions and you'll be on the My Styles tab, there will be a button that you can turn off and on that should make the theme work. If it doesn't, you'll have to restart your browser or device. 3rd option is the final option and usually solves it, you have to go the chrome extension page, click here, then you uninstall stylish and then install it again, and then choose your favourite working styles on here, if you're genuinely stuck, do ask in the comments below with a description of your problem, I'll respond within two days at the max. 1 March 2023 - Released.
